      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 23 article about play Spinning Into Butter (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on July 23 about the play ''Spinning Into Butter'' misstated the original publication date of the children's book ''The Story of Little Black Sambo.'' It was 1899, not 1921.</p>
      </block>
